{"tid":470163,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[靚字巴打] 絲打們會唔會對寫字靚嘅巴打會加分","createTime":"2017-11-16T05:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T13:12:15.000Z","uid":73231,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"db09d8979a4741e124ba9c0c57a6796dbd824c9f","tid":470163,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:00:23.000Z","msg":"今日見到個男同事啲字真係醜得好緊要<br />\n係連睇佢寫乜都好有難度<br />\n<br />\n記憶中好多女仔啲字唔靚但都起碼清楚<br />\n但有啲男仔啲字簡直係醜得可憐<br />\n<br />\n之前幫暑假返咗香港幫中學生補咗陣英文都係普遍女仔字靚好多<br />\n但偶爾都有一兩個男仔啲字好靚<br />\n絕對加哂分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醜字男同事係白鬼<br />\n醜字真係無分國界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400b4321897d281c881f4b362869344b42188dfc","tid":470163,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1314dafe9f88f20ac8b94ff40bc7b86da65ee807","tid":470163,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"寫字反映左一個人做野嘅態度"},{"pid":"1d069ae0bfa8a163cbed9a99ccd05f0196a686d3","tid":470163,"uid":2720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:09:30.000Z","msg":"會對靚字嘅靚仔巴打加分"},{"pid":"e48e6073927eb3d5bb32bfe75f3a1d5c9b320dcb","tid":470163,"uid":75041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"巴<br />\n<br />\n我啲字成日比人話似女仔字<br />\n一筆一劃都好仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿頭寫字好潦但又未到龍飛鳳舞咁<br />\n但睇落去好舒服好清晰<br />\n<br />\n利申：同阿頭都係樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5607765182750d4992f2e6bd1c5c9c55906fa348","tid":470163,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴<br />\n<br />\n我啲字成日比人話似女仔字<br />\n一筆一劃都好仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿頭寫字好潦但又未到龍飛鳳舞咁<br />\n但睇落去好